  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Although widely used, there is a lack of evidence concerning diagnostic value of C-reactive
      protein (CRP) in the postoperative course. The aim of this study was to evaluate the
      diagnostic accuracy of CRP for postoperative inflammatory complications after
      gastroesophageal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
